OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777659064
OL,3,CFormer prison tutor jailed after
OL,4,Cadmitting relationship with serving
OL,5,Cprisoner
OL,7,FA former prison tutor has been jailed
OL,8,Fafter admitting she had a sexual
OL,9,Frelationship with a serving prisoner.
OL,11,FKelly Duffey, 36, of Amesbury,
OL,12,FWiltshire, was handed a 12 month
OL,13,Fprison sentence for two counts of
OL,14,Fmisconduct in public office.
OL,16,FBetween July and September 2024,
OL,17,Fwhilst working at HMP Erlestoke in
OL,18,FWiltshire, Duffey entered into an
OL,19,Fintimate relationship with Ashley
OL,20,FGoodridge, 38, formerly of London.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
