FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777659064
OL,3,CFormer prison tutor jailed after
OL,4,Cadmitting relationship with serving
OL,5,Cprisoner
OL,7,FDuring the investigation counter
OL,8,Fcorruption officers from the South
OL,9,FWest Regional Organised Crime Unit
OL,10,Fsearched Goodridge's cell and found a
OL,11,Fmobile phone which he had used to
OL,12,Fcommunicate with Duffey.
OL,14,FHe pleaded guilty to having and using
OL,15,Fan illicit mobile phone and has had
OL,16,Fhis current prison sentence extended
OL,17,Fby 12 months.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
