OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777659064
OL,3,CFormer prison tutor jailed after
OL,4,Cadmitting relationship with serving
OL,5,Cprisoner
OL,7,FSWROCU Counter Corruption Investigator
OL,8,FPC Mark Paterson said: "The conduct
OL,9,Fdisplayed by Kelly Duffey will not be
OL,10,Ftolerated within a prison estate.
OL,12,F"She may not have been a prison
OL,13,FOfficer or directly employed by HMPPS,
OL,14,Fbut she was in a position of trust as
OL,15,Fan education tutor, a key role in
OL,16,Fprisoner rehabilitation. She
OL,17,Fmisconducted herself and neglected her
OL,18,Fduty over an extended period of time,
OL,19,Fwhich compromised the safety of other
OL,20,Fstaff and inmates."
OL,26,@pD@XOU|D@SO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
