FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777659064
OL,3,CFormer prison tutor jailed after
OL,4,Cadmitting relationship with serving
OL,5,Cprisoner
OL,7,FAndrew Eddy of the Crown Prosecution
OL,8,FService said: "Those working in
OL,9,Fprisons are trusted to uphold strict
OL,10,Fprofessional boundaries between
OL,11,Fthemselves and inmates.
OL,13,F"Duffey's actions amounted to a
OL,14,Fserious breach of that trust and fell
OL,15,Fwell below the standards expected of
OL,16,Fprison staff."
OL,26,@pD@OOUuD@AOUxD@NO]
